The '''Harrin Trade Corridor''', also known as the '''Harrin Run''',<ref name="AE11">{{JournalCite|11|Alien Encounters (article series)}}</ref> was a [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperspace route]] that connected [[Harrin sector/Legends|Harrin sector]] in the [[Inner Rim/Legends|Inner Rim]] to [[Merkat]] in the [[Expansion Region/Legends|Expansion Region]].

Systems along the way included [[Cerenia system/Legends|Cerenia system]], [[Lazerian system/Legends|Lazerian system]], [[Arrgaw system/Legends|Arrgaw system]] and [[Lohopa system/Legends|Lohopa system]].

The [[Kira Run]] split off towards [[Kira's sun|Kira]], which continued into the [[Enarc Run/Legends|Enarc Run]].

